68. Write a Java program to create a new string of 4 copies of the last 3 characters of the original string. The length of the original string must be 3 and above. 

KeyTakeAway
strName.substring(strName.length()-3) //Last 3 char


//<OWN METHOD>
public class w3{
    public static void main(String[] args){
        String main = "Python 3.0";
        String last3 = main.substring(main.length()-3);
        System.out.println(last3 + last3 + last3);
    }
}

